divs: Sighting Detailshello dont know if this is correct emai adrress any ways will like to share my ufo story. first i dont belive in men from out of space but me and my son we saw something very strange in was very close to us we were playing golf in lewisville tx it was geting dark golf course is by the lake we were very far from clubhouse it flew rigth above our heads about 1000 feet we were the only golfers left this object was dark with no ligth at all did not make any noise at all it had like a shield around it in a circle shape that you could verly see we did not see windows or any indication that it was a plane or your typical ufos that you see on tv it was just a solid dark object my son is 15 so i acted like no big deal but to be honest i did get scared science we were to far from club house this happen about 2month ago and i wanted to see if maybe someone else saw the same thing we did.
